        {
            "title": "A股午後跌幅擴大  跌約1% 一周累計跌0.7%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A股午後跌幅擴大，滬股曾跌逾1%，深股跌0.9%，兩市成交合計24003.17億元(人民幣‧下同)，全周計回落約0.7%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-11.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-11.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬綜指收報4095，跌33點或0.82%，最高見4134，升5點或0.12%，午後低見4086，跌43點或1.04%，為全日低位，成交10639.18億元。全周計跌0.7%或29點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深成指收報14280，跌94點或0.65%，上午高見14454點，升80點或0.56%，為全日高位，下午臨收市報14245，跌129點或0.9%，成交13363.99億元。全周跌108點或0.76%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300收跌18點或0.39%，報4669，創業板指數收跌7點或0.22%，報3310點。</p>\n</div>",
